{"tid":1024774,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"[魔獸世界私服]香港公會 就快到一週年啦!!!","createTime":"2019-02-16T20:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T11:50:55.000Z","uid":73938,"like":9,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"06c479703a31a3b5c4d567e94fe8e7dea52da7b5","tid":1024774,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T20:59:40.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/001013_7e06527c6a1fbdffc65741d7e07f0cc4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F001013_7e06527c6a1fbdffc65741d7e07f0cc4.png&h=a95bd7df&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">我地玩緊嘅私服係叫做Warmane , 而80級版本嘅伺服器係容納一萬二千人每晚嘅大型伺服器，可能比起台服仲多人啲。入面比較少bug，而且七倍經驗三倍聲望適合冇時間升Lv嘅朋友。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">因伺服器限制12K人數嘅關係而且伺服器位於歐洲，所以香港時間8點左右就會開始需要排隊進入遊戲</span></strong></span></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/15/001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F15%2F001344_ad7a0e498fb6844a04f96291bfc89dc2.png&h=9378c4e3&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">介紹：<br />\n<br />\n由一群喜愛遊玩80級版本嘅香港人組成嘅群組，自2017年小群組分裂後在，再經過香港私服嘅磨合，組成左一個全新嘅香港公會，而公會已經成功成立就快接近一年時間，中途各位團員都有keep住聯絡同一齊打副本，期待你地嘅加入。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">-Discord群：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/5GCg2Sj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2F5GCg2Sj&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=75879959\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/5GCg2Sj</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-註冊帳號：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.warmane.com/account/create\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.warmane.com%2Faccount%2Fcreate&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=7290707e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.warmane.com/account/create</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-遊戲下載：</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE%2Fview&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=1766e715\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/0B1PMTqz8Q3oiLTlNQnZPbmNtakE/view</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-註冊完/下載完仲差幾步就玩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Step.1 下載登錄器<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU&d=gHg%2Fa1kZgicCxdd1JZL7L6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=15093d4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=0ByaZD-JCOHVOQ2VSc2lpblFheEU</a><br />\nStep.2 放係遊戲主目錄開啟<br />\nStep.3 開Game就可以玩啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如有問題歡迎入Discord咨詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">-最近公會進度</span>：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">25人ICC (12NM/12) (7HC/12)<br />\n25HTOC (4/5)<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yciZHpi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyciZHpi.png&h=42a3aa7b&s={SIZE}\" /></div></span></span><br />\n[/teal]"},{"pid":"48568001c967816594801d8d0640f0496cdbbdca","tid":1024774,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-16T21:00:09.000Z","msg":"DEL漏野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930b2d77061b3d636b8899359211788b27cf33af","tid":1024774,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-17T09:01:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a27e6d30a151a820bc95bf664818297388726c4a","tid":1024774,"uid":73938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T09:07:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a1edbf584211a00ab394b48e93d762410df2825e","tid":1024774,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T01:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79847458e0a4e035b13425b7918a8b141a385f3f","tid":1024774,"uid":214770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"Mac得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"934abf581f1d2d0054620b990d1518648bb3c2df","tid":1024774,"uid":135661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T09:43:52.000Z","msg":"ping大約幾多到?"},{"pid":"bba94d0a18de19805959aa24d1a74b97355eec1d","tid":1024774,"uid":73938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"79847458e0a4e035b13425b7918a8b141a385f3f","tid":1024774,"uid":214770,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-19T06:18:38.000Z","msg":"Mac得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTi